Charles Chukwuma Soludo bụ onye na-azọ ọkwa gọvanọ Anambra steeti n'okpuru pati APGA.
A mụrụ ya n'ụbọchị 28 nke ọnwa Julaị 1960, n'ezinaụlọ Nze Nwankwo Simeon Soludo na Oriakụ Mgbafor Soludo, nke obodo Ụmụeze dị n'Isuọfịa, n'okpuru ọchịchị Agụata dị n'Anambra steeti.
Aha otutu ya bụ Charley Nwamgbafọ.

Soludo gụtara asambodo ọkammụta n'ihe gbasara Akụnaụba obodo (Economics) na mahadum Naịjiria dị na Nsukka ma na mahadum ndị dị na mba ofesi, chịrị ụlọakụ kachasị na Naịjiria bụ Central Bank of Nigeria site n’afọ 2004 ruo 2009.
Anambra election update: O nweghi ntuliaka e mere na Ihiala chaa chaa
Anambra election result: Inec ekwupụtala onyeisi nchịkọta mpụtara ntuliaka Anambra bụ Ọkammụta Florence Banku Obi
Ya na nwunye ya bụ Nonye Queen Frances Soludo mụtara ụmụ isii.
Ka ọ dị ugbua, Soludo na-emeri n'okpuru ọchịchị iri na otu (11) n'ime iri abụọ na otu (21) dị n'Anambra steeti ugbua, dịka ụlọọrụ Inec si kpọpụta.
Nke a abụghị mbụ ọ na-apụta ịzọ ọkwa gọvanọ n’Anambra steeti dịka ọ nwara n’afọ 2010 n’okpuru PDP, mana Peter Obi meriri ya.
Ọ nwakwara n’afọ 2013 n’okpuru APGA, mana ndị nnyocha otu pati ahụ kwuru na o tozughi.
